ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of KELVIN Ng of Edmonton, Alberta, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Oryssia J. Lennie, whose term has expired.
